			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				For the sleeves you will need:<BR>
<BR>
First the Rune of Ivy from &#8220;Grimfeather&#8221; in North Karana. He spawns near the Gypsy camp. He is about level 35 or so. A full group of 30+ can take him pretty easy.<BR>
<BR>
Second you will need the Heart of Fire from the &#8220;Inferno Goblin Wizard&#8221;, also a rare drop from other Inferno Goblins. The Goblin wizard can be found in the castle of the Goblins in Sol A. A good way to do this is with a good group of 28 &#8211; 30+, jump down to the castle entrance from the &#8220;window room&#8221;, have a puller pull from the castle. Be careful of the Wizards as they can hit HARD. They use fire based spells so bring your fire resistance stuff with you.<BR>
<BR>
Next you need two star rubies.<BR>
<BR>
Hope that helps.<BR>
<BR>
Taleran Skylark, 30th Ranger<BR>
Leader of the Ashenwood Elite, Erollisi Marr<BR>

